sub_title: Reporting Project Manager - Fugro Netherlands Marine B.V.
summary:
My experience includes a variety of fieldwork during my MSc in Geophysical and Marine Geology and five rewarding years in the offshore industry which have displayed my excellent initiative, organizational and communication skills. 
Currently I'm a senior member of the client deliverables team at Fugro, working on complex windfarm projects. In the future I am focused on further improving my management and technical ability in the oil and gas and renewables industry as a team member to apply my knowledge, energy and motivation.
